<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Course Completion Certificate - TechTonic</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
      "
    >
      <!-- Logo -->
      <div style="background-color: #1a73e8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px">
        <img
          src="https://i.imgur.com/PqkQ4C1.png"
          alt="TechTonic Logo"
          style="width: 100px; height: auto"
        />
      </div>

      <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 20px">
        Congratulations on Completing Your Course!
      </h2>
      <p>
        We're thrilled to inform you that you've successfully completed
        <strong><%= courseName %></strong>. Your dedication and hard work have
        paid off!
      </p>

      <!-- Certificate Details -->
      <div
        style="
          background-color: #f9f9f9;
          border-radius: 8px;
          padding: 15px;
          margin: 20px 0;
          text-align: left;
        "
      >
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1a73e8">Certificate Details:</h3>
        <p><strong>Course:</strong> <%= courseName %></p>
        <p><strong>Instructor:</strong> <%= instructorName %></p>
        <p><strong>Course Duration:</strong> <%= courseDuration %> hours</p>
        <p><strong>Completion Date:</strong> <%= completionDate %></p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Your certificate of completion is attached to this email. You can also
        access it through your profile on our platform.
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 30px">
        <a
          href="<%= certificateUrl %>"
          style="
            background-color: #1a73e8;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
          "
          target="_blank"
          download="certificate.pdf"
          >View Certificate</a
        >
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 20px">
        Continue your learning journey with us by exploring more courses on our
        platform!
      </p>

      <div
        style="
          margin-top: 40px;
          padding-top: 20px;
          border-top: 1px solid #eee;
          color: #777;
          font-size: 12px;
        "
      >
        <p>
          If you have any questions about your certificate, please contact our
          support team.
        </p>
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TechTonic. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>